Package gov.nist.secauto.decima.core.assessment.result

Interface BaseRequirementResult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    RequirementResult
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultBaseRequirementResult
    public interface BaseRequirementResult
extends RequirementResult
    Represents the compiled results of evaluating all derived requirements associated with a given BaseRequirement.

    If the associated base requirement is not within the assessment scope, then the RequirementResult.getStatus() method is expected to return ResultStatus.NOT_IN_SCOPE. If the base requirement does not specify a set of DerivedRequirement objects, then the RequirementResult.getStatus() method is expected to return ResultStatus.NOT_TESTED, indicating that the test is not implemented.
